Name: 50 Rounds
About the game: Do you think you have what it takes to fight through 50 rounds of zombies and bosses..? I doubt it. Features 5 Unique bosses 6 Different weapons ( more coming soon! ) Zombies get stronger each wave Killing zombies will give you EXP and Coins to spend on either new weapons, ammo or tomes for stat points. - Marksmanship will increase the damage you do, Toughness your Max HP & HP Regen, and Agility will improve your move speed, You will also increase some stats each time you level up
